        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Maintaining Our Resolve to Defend, Encourage, and Conserve our Alliance with Israel Resolution or the MORDECAI Resolution</b></p> <p>This resolution expresses the sense of the House of Representatives that Israel is a crucial ally of the United States and that anti-Semitism and hostility against Israel should be rejected in all forms.</p>]]>
